data.description: Nestled in a serene and sought-after Clearview Estates neighborhood, this magnificent residence offers luxury, comfort, and outdoor entertainment. Situated on an expansive lot, this home boasts many impressive features that will delight any buyer. The interior of this home has been thoughtfully updated, showcasing a modern and stylish design. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring quartz waterfall countertops and ample storage space. The updated flooring enhances the home's aesthetic appeal, while the new AC unit ensures year-round comfort. Step into your private oasis, where a lush, meticulously landscaped yard surrounds a sparkling pool and spa. Perfect for relaxation and recreation, The sports court provides a space for friendly competition and fitness enthusiasts. Entertaining is a breeze with the addition of a sleek bar area. Whether hosting friends for a casual gathering or celebrating special occasions, this space is sure to be a crowd-pleaser. The open floor plan allows for seamless flow between indoor and outdoor spaces, making it ideal for hosting gatherings of all sizes. This home is not only a paradise in itself but also conveniently located near shopping and the breathtaking Lake Pleasant. Enjoy easy access to retail therapy, dining options, and recreational activities, all within a short drive. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional property your own. Experience the luxury of a private pool and spa, the thrill of your own sports court, and the convenience of updated amenities, all in a prime location.
